overview:
Established in the year 2003, we, Honour Engineering Pvt. Ltd, have consolidated a firm space for ourselves in the market spaces and have been widely recognized and known as one of the reputed manufacturers of a wide range of ladder type cable trays and accessories.

Our Team: We have always given due importance to the professionalism and in offering a completely qualitative range, we have hire for ourselves a team of expert professionals.

Quality Assurance: Laying special emphasis on quality of the products, we have tries to make this very sure that only best grade material goes in to the manufacturing of these trays and bents.

Our Infrastructure: We have developed for ourselves a wide and sprawling infrastructure that has always been the major power hose of all our production process.

Research and Development: We have set up a specific R&D wing at our premises in order to carryout all the research activities related to our trade. This wing is equipped with all the amenities and facilities required for successfully accomplishing our researches.

Client Satisfaction: We have made this as our prime objective that through all our product offerings, we have to attain the utmost recognition and satisfaction of our customers.
